00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:58,000
If you try to sterilize surgical instruments after autopsy of a CJD patient,

333
00:36:58,000 --> 00:37:03,000
you've got to raise the temperature to 600 or 700 degrees before you will kill these things.

334
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:12,000
They last in a pasture. If a deer loses saliva that's infected with prions onto a pasture,

335
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:18,000
then those deer are removed. Two years later, a new herd of deer are put on the pasture.

336
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:26,000
And those new herd of deer will come down with that disease because the prions remain infectious in the pasture for up to a couple of years.

337
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:35,000
So, you know, not only is this mysterious prion breaking all the rules in molecular biology and all of that, but it's also indestructible.

