00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:38,000
do have an effect on the kinds of shape that it can adopt in the cell and therefore have an effect on species transmission.

352
00:39:38,000 --> 00:39:49,000
So it may be simply, for example, that the sheep Scrapey is much more difficult for it to transmit to humans than, say, the cow variant.

353
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:56,000
But it may be easier to transmit from sheep to cattle and then cattle to humans. We don't know that.

