00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:20,000
So when you've got that kind of level of knowledge base with respect to this,

357
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:29,000
making confident statements and making confident predictions about, oh, yeah, this has nothing to do with mad cow disease is way premature.

